---
import { MousePointerClick, ShieldCheck, TrendingUp } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<!-- --- BENEFITS --- -->
<section id="beneficios" class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Por qué elegir MPA
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg">
                Diseñado pensando en las necesidades reales del martillero
                público y la inmobiliaria moderna.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Benefit 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group"
            >
                <div
                    class="text-blue-700 mb-6 bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm border border-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                >
                    <ShieldCheck />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                    Confianza Certificada
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Solo profesionales matriculados. Creamos un entorno seguro
                    donde el cliente final sabe que opera con expertos.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Benefit 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group"
            >
                <div
                    class="text-blue-700 mb-6 bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm border border-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                >
                    <MousePointerClick size={24} />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                    Leads Calificados
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Filtros avanzados que pre-cualifican al interesado antes de
                    que llegue a tu WhatsApp. Menos curiosos, más clientes.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Benefit 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 group"
            >
                <div
                    class="text-blue-700 mb-6 bg-white w-16 h-16 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm border border-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
                >
                    <TrendingUp/>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">
                    Visibilidad Potenciada
                </h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Posicionamiento SEO local y campañas de branding digital
                    incluidas para que tus propiedades destaquen.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
